    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.03290.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <handShift rend="printed"/>  
                    <name type="place">The North American Review.</name>
                    <name type="place"><hi rend="italic">30 Lafayette Place.</hi></name>
                    <name type="place"><hi rend="italic">ALLEN THORNDIKE RICE,</hi> <lb/><hi rend="italic">Editor and Proprietor.</hi></name>
                    <name type="place"><hi rend="italic">New York City,</hi></name>
                    <date when="1885-10-23"><handShift rend="manuscript"/>Oct. 23, <handShift
                            rend="printed"/>1885.</date>
                    <!-- letterhead includes seal explaining a dictated letter -->
                </dateline>
                <handShift rend="manuscript"/>
                <salute>My Dear Walt Whitman:</salute>
            </opener>
            <p> I am very, very sorry to learn that your physical condition is so low and that it
                prevents you from doing much work. What I want to know is whether, if I send a
                stenographer over to you, he could do your work, that is to say, could you dictate
                with perfect ease the article on Lincoln and such other articles as you may have
                intended for the North American Review, or any other of Mr. Rice's<ptr
                    target="loc.02206_n4"/> literary enterprises. I think I can manage to give you
                this help if you could utilize it.<ptr target="loc.03290_n1"/>
            </p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Very truly yours,</salute>
                <signed>Jas Redpath</signed>
                <salute></salute>
                <salute>Walt Whitman, <choice><abbr>Esq.</abbr><expan>Esquire</expan></choice></salute>
                <address><addrLine>Camden, N. J.</addrLine></address>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.03290.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
    </text>
